@startuml
title ATM Control - Withdrawal Process

[*] --> Idle

state Idle
state WaitingForAmountSelection
state ProcessingWithdrawalRequest
state DispensingCash
state PrintingReceipt
state EjectingCard
state TerminatingTransaction

Idle : entry / Display Welcome
ClosedDown : entry / Display System Down

Idle --> WaitingForAmountSelection : Card Inserted / Get PIN

WaitingForAmountSelection --> ValidatingPIN : PIN Entered / Validate PIN
ValidatingPIN --> Confiscating : Invalid PIN / Confiscate, Update Status
ValidatingPIN --> WaitingForAmountSelection : Invalid PIN Prompt
ValidatingPIN --> ProcessingWithdrawalRequest : Valid PIN / Display Menu

WaitingForAmountSelection --> EjectingCard : Cancel / Eject

ProcessingWithdrawalRequest --> DispensingCash : Withdrawal Selected / Request Withdrawal, Display Wait
DispensingCash --> PrintingReceipt : Cash Dispensed / Print Receipt, Display Cash Dispensed, Confirm Cash Dispensed
PrintingReceipt --> EjectingCard : Rejected / Eject, Display Apology

Confiscating --> TerminatingTransaction : Card Confiscated / Display Confiscated
EjectingCard --> TerminatingTransaction : Card Ejected / Display Ejected

TerminatingTransaction --> Idle : After (Elapsed Time) [Closedown Not Requested]
TerminatingTransaction --> ClosedDown : After (Elapsed Time) [Closedown Was Requested]

@enduml
